            <h3 class="w_a_headding"><strong>Wolverine Access</strong></h3>
            <ul class="blk_text">
                <li>Wolverine Access provides students with all required textbooks each semester for a low bundled flat rate of $250 for fall, $250 for spring, and $150 for summer. The bundled flat rate will be posted to student tuition and fee accounts each semester.</li>
                <li>Eligible students will begin each semester with complete access to required textbooks no later than the first day of classes. Digital books are delivered within Canvas, while all print books will be distributed by the UVU Store.</li>
                <li>Students can log in to Canvas to view program options, including how to opt out.</li>
            </ul>


